\[ \text{score} = (\text{attack} \times 0.3) + (\text{defence} \times 0.25) + (\text{speed} \times 0.2) + (\text{intelligence} \times 0.15) + (\text{tech} \times 0.1) \]

   Reasoning: Iron Man has high intelligence and tech, which contribute significantly to his score.
